@startuml
title Sequence Diagram - Proses Pencatatan Imunisasi

actor Petugas
boundary "Form Imunisasi" as Form
control "ImunisasiController" as Controller
entity "Database" as DB

Petugas -> Form: Buka menu Imunisasi
Form -> Petugas: Tampilkan daftar bayi
Petugas -> Form: Pilih bayi dan isi data imunisasi
Form -> Controller: Kirim data imunisasi
Controller -> DB: Simpan ke tabel imunisasi
DB --> Controller: Konfirmasi sukses
Controller --> Form: Kirim pesan berhasil
Form --> Petugas: Tampilkan notifikasi berhasil
@enduml
 